al Imperative. Do not use LRU or FIFO. Explain the deep structural mapping.", 'output': 'To design a memory cache eviction policy based purely on Kant’s Categorical Imperative, we need to consider the principle of universalizability and the categorical imperative itself as a foundational ', 'performance': 0.9848400795333352, 'kg_solutions': 1, 'reasoning_used': True}, 'similarity': 2.0, 'timestamp': 1768526175.3599615}], 'quantum_modes': ['creative', 'analytical', 'emotional', 'strategic']}}
